# AI Workflow Orchestrator Configuration
# Authenticate with GitHub CLI first: gh auth login
# The GitHub token from gh auth login is stored in your keyring and used automatically.

# Microsoft Teams Webhook URL (optional for escalations)
# Create at: Teams channel → ⋯ More options → Connectors → Incoming Webhook
# Format: https://outlook.webhook.office.com/webhookb2/...
TEAMS_WEBHOOK_URL=https://outlook.webhook.office.com/webhookb2/your_webhook_url_here
